    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SAN FRANCISCO and OAKLAND\nHELICOPTER AIRLINES\nJet-Powered Sikorsky S-62 — 10 passenger\nAmphibious Helicopter above San Francisco and\nay Bridge.\nSFO AIRLINES operates frequent scheduled serv-\nice between the Airports and Heliports in San\nFrancisco, Oakland, Berkeley and Palo Alto. Bay-\ncircling Scenic Excursion Trips are also offered.\nPhones: YU 1-7750 and TE 2-3606\n1966\nMike Roberta\nBERKELEY 2, CALIF.\nE. F. Clements, 85 Bluxome St., San Francisco, Calif. 94107\nC9528A\nв 2,00\n2015."
    ],
